This project determines if the given triangle is EQUILATERAL, SCALERE or ISOSCELES triangle.

The project is built using maven. The build instructions assume that you have maven installed locally on the system. If not please install it.

Please follow the below steps to build and run locally
 1) Clone or download this project on to your local machine
 2) go to the root folder of the project
 3) open terminal and run mvn clean install

 Clean install task will run the junits automatically.
